-22 17-52-35 (0-00-06-47).png", "id": "297589002391485", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57572948_297589012391484_3787102876524498545_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MqFiH-AqBQgQ7kNvgHhnU8s&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAmcf15q9NRdT6jMsCmk1gv_AD0cBufE4wT7BzGCwolwQ&oe=6737307D"}, {"file_name": "2022-01-22 17-52-35 (0-00-05-11).png", "id": "1084353699016907", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984447_1084353702350240_2933415590870248678_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=d701rX2eyIwQ7kNvgFFC6S3&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBKiyxsGhVc4NOWT5Rfi8QODH58GM4Ccf-ASfWxDkOThw&oe=673734F2"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CoverImageSafeAreaTemplateLandscape_2560x1440 new.png", "id": "445289890711681", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031629_445289894045014_2099929920867611179_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LcdlGokJVfQQ7kNvgFmWRmP&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA5VdBDaY7CgKfmi6T40Iry6TwKnsjLTHuQIm9zKpgyEQ&oe=67371B11"}, "display_name": "Brisk Square", "keywords": [], "long_description": "The only Infinite Run game in VR!\nChallenge your friends in an infinite run gameplay and see who emerges victorious. Enter a cyberpunk world and enjoy multiple game modes:\n\nMultiplayer Mode\nCampaign Mode\nDual Wield Mode\nBrisk Mode\n\nFuture! In the wake of a cataclysm! You are the prey in a world full of hunters. Run, overpower them and free the violent streets in this intensively fast-paced cyber adventure. Be the decisive last stand in an infinite run gameplay by starting with a simple blade and evolve step by step to unlock more advanced weapons. Make your way ahead in the game by sword-slashing with your one hand and use superior powers to push/pull/crash objects with your other one and collect enough points to reach the top of a worldwide leaderboar